OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start with
OL,6,Fa touch of frost possible. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells will turn hazy during the day
OL,8,Fas cloud thickens from the west,
OL,9,Fpatchy light rain developing through
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain pushing
OL,13,Feastwards, mostly light and patchy,
OL,14,Fbut the odd heavier burst possible in
OL,15,Fthe west. Turning more showery
OL,16,Fovernight, some drier and clearer
OL,17,Fspells by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
