OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the brightness for East
OL,7,FLothian and the eastern Borders during
OL,8,Fthe morning. The showers could be
OL,9,Fheavy, perhaps the odd rumble of
OL,10,Fthunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry and bright on Monday with early
OL,14,Fshowers dying out. Rain or showers on
OL,15,FTuesday and Wednesday, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
